<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>한화투자증권 · 시장 브리핑 2026.04.15</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg:#0a0c10; --bg2:#111318; --bg3:#181c23; --bg4:#1e2229;
    --border:rgba(255,255,255,0.07); --border2:rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    --text:#f0f2f5; --text2:#8a8f9a; --text3:#555b67;
    --up:#ff6b3d; --up-bg:rgba(255,107,61,0.1); --up-border:rgba(255,107,61,0.3);
    --dn:#4a9eff; --dn-bg:rgba(74,158,255,0.1); --dn-border:rgba(74,158,255,0.3);
    --accent:#ff6b3d; --gold:#f0c060; --green:#4ecb8a;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
  body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;min-height:100vh;}
  body::before{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(255,107,61,0.015) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,107,61,0.015) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:40px 40px;pointer-events:none;}
  .app{position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 24px;}

  .header{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:36px;padding-bottom:24px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
  .header-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;}
  .logo-mark{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),#ff9c6e);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:#fff;}
  .header-title h1{font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-0.3px;}
  .header-title p{font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);margin-top:2px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;}
  .header-meta{text-align:right;}
  .header-date{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);}
  .ai-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;margin-top:6px;font-size:10px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:20px;border:1px solid var(--up-border);color:var(--accent);background:var(--up-bg);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;}
  .ai-badge::before{content:'';width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);animation:pulse 2s infinite;}
  @keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1;}50%{opacity:0.3;}}

  .metrics{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:12px;margin-bottom:24px;}
  .metric{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:border-color 0.2s;}
  .metric:hover{border-color:var(--border2);}
  .metric::before{content:attr(data-rank);position:absolute;right:12px;top:10px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--text3);}
  .metric-label{font-size:10px;color:var(--text2);letter-spacing:0.3px;margin-bottom:6px;text-transform:uppercase;}
  .metric-value{font-size:22px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.5px;}
  .metric-sub{font-size:10px;color:var(--text2);margin-top:4px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;}
  .metric-value.up{color:var(--up);}

  .nav{display:flex;gap:4px;margin-bottom:20px;}
  .nav-btn{padding:7px 16px;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:transparent;color:var(--text2);font-size:12px;font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.15s;}
  .nav-btn:hover{background:var(--bg3);color:var(--text);}
  .nav-btn.active{background:var(--accent);color:#fff;border-color:var(--accent);}

  .panel{display:none;}
  .panel.active{display:block;animation:fadeIn 0.2s ease;}
  @keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(4px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}

  .grid2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-bottom:14px;}
  .split-layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 400px;gap:16px;align-items:start;}

  .card{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:18px 20px;transition:border-color 0.2s;}
  .card:hover{border-color:var(--border2);}
  .card-title{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;margin-bottom:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;}
  .card-title .dot{width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;}

  .stock-row{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:9px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
  .stock-row:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
  .stock-row.clickable{cursor:pointer;border-radius:8px;padding:9px 8px;margin:0 -8px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);transition:background 0.15s;}
  .stock-row.clickable:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
  .stock-row.clickable:hover{background:var(--bg3);}
  .stock-row.clickable.selected{background:var(--bg4);border-left:2px solid var(--accent) !important;padding-left:10px;margin-left:-10px;}
  .stock-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;}
  .stock-mkt{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);margin-top:1px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;}
  .stock-price{font-size:12px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;color:var(--text2);}
  .badge-up{font-size:11px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-weight:500;color:var(--up);background:var(--up-bg);border:1px solid var(--up-border);border-radius:6px;padding:2px 7px;white-space:nowrap;}
  .badge-dn{font-size:11px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-weight:500;color:var(--dn);background:var(--dn-bg);border:1px solid var(--dn-border);border-radius:6px;padding:2px 7px;white-space:nowrap;}

  /* NEWS SIDE PANEL */
  .news-panel{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;position:sticky;top:20px;transition:border-color 0.2s;}
  .news-panel.active-panel{border-color:var(--up-border);}
  .news-panel-header{padding:13px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;background:var(--bg3);}
  .news-panel-title{font-size:10px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;}
  .news-powered{font-size:9px;color:var(--text3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;}
  .news-powered::before{content:'';width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--green);animation:pulse 2s infinite;}
  .news-stock-bar{padding:11px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;}
  .news-stock-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);}
  .news-stock-meta{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;}
  .news-body{padding:14px 16px;min-height:300px;max-height:520px;overflow-y:auto;}

  .news-empty{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;height:280px;gap:10px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;}
  .news-arrow{font-size:24px;opacity:0.3;margin-bottom:4px;}
  .news-empty-text{font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;}
  .news-hint{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;margin-top:2px;}

  .news-loading{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;height:280px;gap:14px;}
  .spinner{width:24px;height:24px;border:2px solid var(--border2);border-top-color:var(--accent);border-radius:50%;animation:spin 0.8s linear infinite;}
  @keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg);}}
  .loading-label{font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;}
  .loading-dots::after{content:'';animation:dots 1.4s steps(4,end) infinite;}
  @keyframes dots{0%{content:'';}25%{content:'.';}50%{content:'..';}75%{content:'...';}100%{content:'';}}

  .news-item{padding:13px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);animation:fadeIn 0.3s ease;}
  .news-item:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
  .news-tag{display:inline-block;font-size:9px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px;margin-bottom:6px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.3px;}
  .tag-news{background:var(--dn-bg);color:var(--dn);border:1px solid var(--dn-border);}
  .tag-disc{background:rgba(240,192,96,0.1);color:var(--gold);border:1px solid rgba(240,192,96,0.3);}
  .tag-analyst{background:rgba(78,203,138,0.1);color:var(--green);border:1px solid rgba(78,203,138,0.3);}
  .news-headline{font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:5px;}
  .news-summary{font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.7;}
  .news-date{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);margin-top:5px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;}

  .news-footer{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);padding:10px 16px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--bg3);line-height:1.5;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;}

  .news-error{padding:24px 16px;text-align:center;color:var(--text3);font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;}
  .news-error strong{color:var(--text2);display:block;margin-bottom:8px;font-size:13px;}

  /* other panels */
  .section-title{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;}
  .section-title::after{content:'';flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--border);}
  .bar-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
  .bar-row:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
  .bar-rank{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);width:16px;text-align:right;flex-shrink:0;}
  .bar-name{font-size:12px;font-weight:500;width:110px;flex-shrink:0;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;}
  .bar-track{flex:1;height:5px;background:var(--bg3);border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden;}
  .bar-fill{height:100%;border-radius:3px;}
  .bar-fill.bar-up{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--up),#ff9c6e);}
  .bar-fill.bar-flat{background:var(--dn);}
  .bar-amount{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);width:72px;text-align:right;flex-shrink:0;}
  .bar-pct{width:50px;text-align:right;flex-shrink:0;}
  .theme-card{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:18px 20px;}
  .theme-header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:12px;}
  .theme-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;}
  .theme-status{font-size:10px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:20px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;}
  .status-strong{background:var(--up-bg);color:var(--up);border:1px solid var(--up-border);}
  .status-mixed{background:rgba(240,192,96,0.1);color:var(--gold);border:1px solid rgba(240,192,96,0.3);}
  .theme-stocks{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;}
  .theme-stock-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:11px;}
  .theme-stock-name{color:var(--text2);}
  .theme-stock-pct{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-weight:500;}
  .theme-reason{margin-top:12px;padding:10px 12px;background:var(--bg3);border-radius:8px;border-left:2px solid var(--accent);font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.7;}
  .summary{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid var(--accent);border-radius:12px;padding:16px 20px;margin-bottom:20px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.8;}
  .summary strong{color:var(--text);font-weight:500;}
  .summary .up-text{color:var(--up);font-weight:500;}
  .donut-wrap{position:relative;height:160px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}
  .donut-label{position:absolute;text-align:center;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);}
  .donut-label .dl-num{font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:var(--up);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;}
  .donut-label .dl-sub{font-size:10px;color:var(--text2);}
  .legend{display:flex;gap:14px;margin-top:10px;justify-content:center;}
  .legend-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);}
  .legend-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:2px;}
  .broker-note{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);padding:10px 14px;background:var(--bg3);border-radius:8px;margin-top:14px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;line-height:1.6;}

  @media(max-width:900px){.split-layout{grid-template-columns:1fr;}.metrics{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}.grid2{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="app">

  <header class="header">
    <div class="header-logo">
      <div class="logo-mark">HW</div>
      <div class="header-title">
        <h1>한화투자증권 시장 브리핑</h1>
        <p>AI 자동 분석 리포트 · Daily Edition</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="header-meta">
      <div class="header-date">2026.04.15 (WED) · 전일 종가 기준</div>
      <div style="display:flex;justify-content:flex-end;margin-top:6px;"><span class="ai-badge">AI 자동 생성</span></div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="metrics">
    <div class="metric" data-rank="01"><div class="metric-label">KOSPI 평균 등락률</div><div class="metric-value up">+1.39%</div><div class="metric-sub">상승 671 · 하락 199 · 보합 80</div></div>
    <div class="metric" data-rank="02"><div class="metric-label">KOSDAQ 평균 등락률</div><div class="metric-value up">+2.19%</div><div class="metric-sub">상승 1,284 · 하락 327 · 보합 212</div></div>
    <div class="metric" data-rank="03"><div class="metric-label">거래대금 1위</div><div class="metric-value" style="font-size:16px;color:var(--text);">SK하이닉스</div><div class="metric-sub" style="color:var(--up);">+6.06% · 5조 2,690억</div></div>
    <div class="metric" data-rank="04"><div class="metric-label">분석 종목 수</div><div class="metric-value" style="color:var(--text);">2,882</div><div class="metric-sub">KOSPI 950 + KOSDAQ 1,823+</div></div>
  </div>

  <nav class="nav">
    <button class="nav-btn active" onclick="showPanel('overview',this)">시장 개요</button>
    <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showPanel('top',this)">급등·급락</button>
    <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showPanel('volume',this)">거래대금</button>
    <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showPanel('theme',this)">테마 분석</button>
    <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showPanel('broker',this)">브로커 추천</button>
  </nav>

  <!-- OVERVIEW -->
  <div class="panel active" id="panel-overview">
    <div class="summary">
      전일 코스피·코스닥 양 시장 <strong>강한 상승</strong>세. 코스닥 평균 <span class="up-text">+2.19%</span>로 코스피 상회.
      <strong>SK하이닉스(+6.06%)</strong>·<strong>삼성전자(+2.74%)</strong>가 시장을 주도했으며,
      <span class="up-text">엔비디아 CEO 광반도체 발언</span> 영향으로 반도체·광통신 관련주 동반 급등.
    </div>
    <div class="grid2">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title"><span class="dot" style="background:var(--up);"></span>KOSPI 시장 현황</div>
        <div class="donut-wrap"><canvas id="kospiChart" width="160" height="160"></canvas><div class="donut-label"><div class="dl-num">70.6%</div><div class="dl-sub">상승 비율</div></div></div>
        <div class="legend"><div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--up);"></div>상승 671</div><div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--dn);"></div>하락 199</div><div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border2);"></div>보합 80</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title"><span class="dot" style="background:#4ecb8a;"></span>KOSDAQ 시장 현황</div>
        <div class="donut-wrap"><canvas id="kosdaqChart" width="160" height="160"></canvas><div class="donut-label"><div class="dl-num" style="color:#4ecb8a;">70.4%</div><div class="dl-sub">상승 비율</div></div></div>
        <div class="legend"><div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#4ecb8a;"></div>상승 1,284</div><div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--dn);"></div>하락 327</div><div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border2);"></div>보합 212</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid2">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title"><span class="dot" style="background:var(--up);"></span>코스피 주요 종목</div>
        <div class="stock-row"><div><div class="stock-name">SK하이닉스</div><div class="stock-mkt">KOSPI · 5조 2,690억</div></div><div style="text-align:right;"><div class="stock-price">1,103,000</div><span class="badge-up">+6.06%</span></div></div>
        <div class="stock-row"><div><div class="stock-name">미래에셋증권</div><div class="stock-mkt">KOSPI · 7,147억</div></div><div style="text-align:right;"><div class="stock-price">72,400</div><span class="badge-up">+10.87%</span></div></div>
        <div class="stock-row"><div><div class="stock-name">SK스퀘어</div><div class="stock-mkt">KOSPI · 4,190억</div></div><div style="text-align:right;"><div class="stock-price">640,000</div><span class="badge-up">+10.34%</span></div></div>
        <div class="stock-row"><div><div class="stock-name">삼성전자</div><div class="stock-mkt">KOSPI · 4조 9,230억</div></div><div style="text-align:right;"><div class="stock-price">206,500</div><span class="badge-up">+2.74%</span></div></div>
        <div class="stock-row"><div><div class="stock-name">SNT에너지</div><div class="stock-mkt">KOSPI · 477억</div></div><div style="text-align:right;"><div class="stock-price">58,100</div><span class="badge-dn">-9.36%</span></div></div>
        <div class="stock-row"><div><div class="stock-name">대우건설</div><div class="stock-mkt">KOSPI · 7,180억</div></div><div style="text-align:right;"><div class="stock-price">39,350</div><span class="badge-dn">-1.05%</span></div></div>
        <div class="stock-row"><div><div class="stock-name">남선알미늄</div><div class="stock-mkt">KOSPI · 4,692억</div></div><div style="text-align:right;"><div class="stock-price">12,450</div><span class="badge-up">+7.50%</span></div></div>
        <div class="stock-row"><div><div class="stock-name">삼성전자우</div><div class="stock-mkt">KOSPI · 4,221억</div></div><div style="text-align:right;"><div class="stock-price">148,500</div><span class="badge-up">+2.09%</span></div></div>
        <div class="stock-row"><div><div class="stock-name">LS ELECTRIC</div><div class="stock-mkt">KOSPI · 4,052억</div></div><div style="text-align:right;"><div class="stock-price">385,000</div><span class="badge-up">+3.57%</span></div></div>
        <div class="stock-row"><div><div class="stock-name">한화투자증권</div><div class="stock-mkt">KOSPI · 1,890억</div></div><div style="text-align:right;"><div class="stock-price">5,890</div><span class="badge-up">+6.93%</span></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title"><span class="dot" style="background:#4ecb8a;"></span>코스닥 주요 종목</div>
        <div class="stock-row"><div><div class="stock-name">퀄리타스반도체</div><div class="stock-mkt">KOSDAQ · 2,351억</div></div><div style="text-align:right;"><div class="stock-price">20,550</div><span class="badge-up">+29.98%</span></div></div>
        <div class="stock-row"><div><div class="stock-name">우리로</div><div class="stock-mkt">KOSDAQ · 5,026억</div></div><div style="text-align:right;"><div class="stock-price">11,860</div><span class="badge-up">+18.72%</span></div></div>
        <div class="stock-row"><div><div class="stock-name">두산테스나</div><div class="stock-mkt">KOSDAQ GLOBAL · 667억</div></div><div style="text-align:right;"><div class="stock-price">97,800</div><span class="badge-up">+11.52%</span></div></div>
        <div class="stock-row"><div><div class="stock-name">빛과전자</div><div class="stock-mkt">KOSDAQ · 2,523억</div></div><div style="text-align:right;"><div class="stock-price">6,390</div><span class="badge-up">+29.88%</span></div></div>
